doctype html
html(lang='en')
    head
        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='Pain Clinic based in Somerset West- headed by world renowned interventional pain practitioner Dr. Louis Smit')
        meta(name='author', content='Dehan Louw')
        meta(name="google-site-verification" content="jx4UxsWEZjQtAJtPkbyF_R1xczPfLZfDAJ1cULruL-4")
        title Pain Clinic based in Somerset West
        // Bootstrap core CSS
        link(href='vendor/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css', rel='stylesheet')
        // Custom fonts for this template
        link(href='vendor/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
        link(href='vendor/simple-line-icons/css/simple-line-icons.css', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:300,400,700,300italic,400italic,700italic', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
        // Custom styles for this template
        link(href='css/stylesheet.min.css', rel='stylesheet')
        //Favicon
        link(rel="icon", href="img/favicon.ico")
    body
        // Navigation
        include navbar.pug
        // Header
        section.header.h-100.d-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-center
            img(src="img/logo.svg", alt="Helderberg Pain Clinic Logo")
        //Intro
        section.intro.content-section.bg-light
            .container
                .row.mb-3
                    .col-md-12
                        h1 Helderberg Pain Clinic in Somerset West
                .row
                    .col-md-8
                        p Pain is a complex phenomenon with which many have to deal with on a daily basis. Often misunderstood and seldom local. It can present dissociatively, behave irratiaclly and is as ilusive to diagnose as it is stuborn to treat.
                        p Helderberg Pain Clinic has built a reputation on understanding, defining and managing the field of pain. We are experts at seeing pain hollistically and solving underlying problems rather than treating superficial
                .form-row.mt-5
                    .col-12.col-md-2
                        a.button.btn.btn-block.btn-lg.btn-info(href="mailto:info@helderbergpainclinic.co.za") Enquire
        // Aboutn
        section#about.about.bg-primary
            .container.pt-5
                h2 Dr. Louis Smit
                h4 Head practitioner at Helderberg Pain Clinic
                p MB.ChB.(Stell) Dip. Obst.(SA), DA(SA), NDT(Sed), FIPP
                hr
                .row.mt-5
                    .col-md-6
                        h4 Professional background
                        p Dr. Louis Smit is an internationally qualified and experience specialist in the field of pain. After completing his undergraduate studies locally, he practiced in Canada, before returning to further his expertise in anesthetics.

                        p He cemented his education by completing his Fellowship in Interventional Pain at the renowned World Institute of Pain in the Netherlands.

                        a.btn.btn-info.text-dark.mb-3(href="img/fipp.pdf", target="_blank")
                            i.icon-book-open
                                span FIPP Certification

                    .col-md-6
                        h4 Personal journey
                        p After being diagnosed with Guillain Barre Syndrome, Dr. Smit is intimately familiar with the path to recovery. Learning to walk, write and live again provided him with a painful, yet irreplacable understanding of the subject.

                        p A combination of education and experience has culminated in a holistic approach to the patient as body, soul and spirit. The Helderberg Pain Clinic shares this view of surpasing a mere biomedical analysis in order to truly help their patients thrive and enjoy lasting vitality.

                .row.pb-5
                    .col-md-3.offset-md-9
                        img.cert-logo(src="img/wip.png", alt="World Institute of Pain Clinic Logo")
        //Services
        section.services.bg-light.text-white.text-center.text-dark
            .container

                .row
                    .col-lg-4
                        .features-icons-item.mx-auto.mb-5.mb-lg-0.mb-lg-3
                            .features-icons-icon.d-flex
                                i.icon-frame.m-auto.text-primary
                            h3 Diagnosis
                            p.lead.mb-0 From narrowing in on the point of pain, to identifying root causes and lifestyle contributers
                    .col-lg-4
                        .features-icons-item.mx-auto.mb-5.mb-lg-0.mb-lg-3
                            .features-icons-icon.d-flex
                                i.icon-people.m-auto.text-primary
                            h3 Treatment
                            p.lead.mb-0 Holistic approach to applying the latest advancements in pain management and treatment
                    .col-lg-4
                        .features-icons-item.mx-auto.mb-0.mb-lg-3
                            .features-icons-icon.d-flex
                                i.icon-refresh.m-auto.text-primary
                            h3 Rehabilitation
                            p.lead.mb-0 Ensuring long term relief and walking the road to recovery together
        // Treatment options
        section#treatment.treatment.bg-light
            .container-fluid.p-0
                .row.no-gutters
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-2.text-white.showcase-img(style="background-image: url('img/RFThumbnail.png');")
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-1.my-auto.showcase-text
                        h2 Cutting edge treatments
                        p.lead.mb-0
                            | We utilise advanced RF technology to provide the latest in targeted pain relief techniques
                        a(href="treatments-radio-frequency.html")
                            i.fa.fa-angle-right.mr-3
                            span Read more
                .row.no-gutters
                    .col-lg-6.text-white.showcase-img(style="background-image: url('img/bg-masthead.jpg');")
                    .col-lg-6.my-auto.showcase-text
                        h2 Ozone therapy
                        p.lead.mb-0
                            | Ozone is not a medication but and adjuvant that helps the body to heal itself
                        a(href="treatments-ozone-therapy.html")
                            i.fa.fa-angle-right.mr-3
                            span Read more
                .row.no-gutters
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-2.text-white.showcase-img(style="background-image: url('img/physicaltherapy.jpeg');")
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-1.my-auto.showcase-text
                        h2 Physical therapy
                        p.lead.mb-0
                            | Massage, Physiotherapy, Pilates, Biokinetics, Chiropractic and TENS treatments
                .row.no-gutters
                    .col-lg-6.text-white.showcase-img(style="background-image: url('img/lifestyle.jpeg');")
                    .col-lg-6.my-auto.showcase-text
                        h2 Lifestyle changes
                        p.lead.mb-0
                            | Guiding patients to manage their issues by means of lifestyle alterations
                .row.no-gutters
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-2.text-white.showcase-img(style="background-image: url('img/psycological.jpeg');")
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-1.my-auto.showcase-text
                        h2 Psycological support
                        p.lead.mb-0
                            | Coping training and stress management- completing the circle of comprehensive pain treatment
                .row.no-gutters
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-1.text-white.showcase-img(style="background-image: url('img/ablative.jpeg');")
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-2.my-auto.showcase-text
                        h2 Open ablative Surgery
                        p.lead.mb-0
                            | Expert surgical intervention for serious cases which dictate more drastic measures
                .row.no-gutters
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-2.text-white.showcase-img(style="background-image: url('img/underlying.jpeg');")
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-1.my-auto.showcase-text
                        h2 Underlying cause treatment
                        p.lead.mb-0
                            | Looking past superficial symptoms to treat the deep seated issues presenting as pain
                .row.no-gutters
                    .col-lg-6.text-white.showcase-img(style="background-image: url('img/analgesia.jpeg');")
                    .col-lg-6.my-auto.showcase-text
                        h2 Analgesia & Adjuvent medication
                        p.lead.mb-0
                            | Complete range of pharmacological interventions, selected with the greatest care and caution
                .row.no-gutters
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-2.text-white.showcase-img(style="background-image: url('img/minimal.jpeg');")
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-1.my-auto.showcase-text
                        h2 Minimally invasive treatments
                        p.lead.mb-0
                            | Quick and comfortable per-cutaneous interventional treatment
                .row.no-gutters
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-1.text-white.showcase-img(style="background-image: url('img/alternative.jpeg');")
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-2.my-auto.showcase-text
                        h2 Alteratives
                        p.lead.mb-0
                            | Various alternative, non-allopathic healers available for all circumstances
        // Locate
        section#locate.locate.content-section.bg-light
            .container.text-center
                h2 Ask for help today
                hr.w-50
                .row.mt-5
                    .col-md-4.text-center.mb-3
                        i.icon.icon-phone.display-4.text-primary
                        p.mt-3 021 851 1556
                    .col-md-4.text-center.mb-3
                        i.icon.icon-location-pin.display-4.text-primary
                        p.mt-3 Paardevlei Specialist Medical Centre
                        p Somerset West
                        a.btn.btn-md.btn-info.mb-3(href="https://www.google.co.za/maps/place/Paardevlei+Specialist+Medical+Centre/@-34.0922013,18.814457,17z/data=!4m8!1m2!2m1!1spaardevlei+specialist+medical+centre!3m4!1s0x1dcdcaa84a596e77:0xc17593b40adab1e5!8m2!3d-34.0920798!4d18.8167353", target="_blank" ) Go To Map
                    .col-md-4.text-center
                        i.icon.icon-envelope.display-4.text-primary
                        a.d-block.mt-3.text-dark(href="mailto:info@helderbergpainclinic.co.za")
                                                    | info@helderbergpainclinic.co.za
        // Footer
        include footer.pug

